'''Orange Powder''' is a powder that allows recharging [[magic points|magic]] and [[life points]] to full capacity. Only fully qualified wizards are able to buy this powder. It is sold by [[Chedil Amiradoo]], who also sells various wizards' accessories. The price of one powder is 10 [[kash]]es.

After [[Twinsen]] finishes his studies in the [[School of Magic]] and becomes a wizard, he can buy such powder from Chedil to fill his life and magic points.

